      "title": {
        "en": "Old Town & Fegina",
        "de": "Was Monterosso besonders macht",
        "fr": "Ce qui rend Monterosso spécial",
        "it": "Il Meglio delle Cinque Terre"
      },
      "subtitle": {
        "en": "Monterosso is divided into two distinct areas connected by a tunnel."
      },
      "content": {
        "en": "The **Old Town** (Centro Storico) features narrow medieval streets, the 13th-century Church of San Giovanni Battista, and authentic trattorias. **Fegina**, the newer section, offers the famous sandy beach, most hotels, and the train station. A short walk or tunnel connects both areas, giving visitors the best of historic charm and beach resort convenience."
      }
    },
